snippet.title: Star Wars: Hunters™ - Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Zynga is proud to announce Star Wars: Hunters™. This competitive arena combat game is coming in 2021 to the Nintendo Switch system and mobile devices. Set after the fall of the Galactic Empire, Star Wars: Hunters will connect players in real time to battle in settings inspired by iconic Star Wars™ locales. Star Wars: Hunters will bring players together to engage in thrilling, squad-based, multiplayer battles featuring a diverse array of distinctive new Star Wars characters. 

Visit www.swhunters.com and receive game updates.
